{
  "stem": "21812.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't recall now whether that was after I was evacuated or whether I started before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I don't think I went to school in Bradford, so I didn't do very much there, from what I recall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But it was a short time, because by September-- I was there two months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And by September 4, I think, or 6, the war started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember listening to King George proclaiming, announcing the beginning of war with Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then very soon afterwards, we were evacuated into a-- into the countryside in a very small town called Colne, Lancashire, C-O-- C-O-L-N-E, Lancashire.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I mentioned to you privately before, I can't remember-- again, I-- I repressed it and I can't remember how I got there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just can't remember whether by train, by bus, by cart, whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and we were-- but I do remember we wound up in a schoolyard.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the parents came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they knew we were-- children were coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Those were British children too, many more British than-- than refugees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the-- the parents came, people and couples came there and picked out the children they wanted to take to their homes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This was what-- how it was done.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "These children who were evacuated wound up in other people's homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so people came and selected the-- the children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, two or three of us were very tall, much taller for our age than different age group, I remember.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we were left over and nobody took us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then finally, the pub owner took two of us, the pub in-- in Colne, Lancashire.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so we went to the pub.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they showed us the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
